# GCP Vertex AI

Primary metrics from GCP Vertex AI service. This dashboard contains: 

- Invocation rates
- Error rates
- Token usage
- Model Invocation latency
- Prediction metrics
- Resource Utilization

embeddableConfig.description: Total number of model invocations (prediction requests).
Top 10 model usage group-by the resource id of the PublisherModel.
embeddableConfig.title: Model usage

embeddableConfig.description: Total error response code of prediction request.
Count of input and output tokens usage over the period group-by top 3 models.
embeddableConfig.title: Token usage - by model deployment

embeddableConfig.description: Total errors over the period group-by top 3 error response codes.
embeddableConfig.title: Overall error rate - by response code

embeddableConfig.description: Count of invocations over the period group-by top 5 model usage.
embeddableConfig.title: Overall invocation rate - by model

embeddableConfig.description: Invocation latency over the period in milliseconds group-by top 5 model usage.
embeddableConfig.title: Model invocation latency - by model

embeddableConfig.description: Consumed throughput count over the period group-by top 5 model usage.
embeddableConfig.title: Consumed throughput - by model

embeddableConfig.description: Number of online predictions over the period group-by endpoint.
embeddableConfig.title: Predictions - by endpoint

embeddableConfig.description: Online prediction latency in milliseconds over the period group-by endpoint.
embeddableConfig.title: Prediction latency - by endpoint

embeddableConfig.description: Number of online prediction errors over the period group-by endpoint.
embeddableConfig.title: Prediction errors - by endpoint

embeddableConfig.description: Fraction of CPU allocated by the deployed model replica and currently in use. May exceed 100% if the machine type has multiple CPUs. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling data is not visible for up to 360 seconds.
embeddableConfig.title: CPU utilization

embeddableConfig.description: Amount of memory allocated by the deployed model replica and currently in use. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling data is not visible for up to 360 seconds.
embeddableConfig.title: Memory usage

embeddableConfig.description: Number of bytes sent and received over the network by the deployed model replica. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling data is not visible for up to 360 seconds.
embeddableConfig.title: Maximum bytes transferred
